description: Try our easy to follow Mandarin & Almond Cake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Mandarin & Almond Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Decorate cake with mandarin segments and drizzle over candied peel and syrup. Serve. Note: Mandarins are in season April - October.
